e.com\/"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png"},{"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Go to the website and learn things at ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" is also available there to get icons for your projects.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-2.png","code":null},{"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-3.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Have a look ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki"},{"text":" to discover how OUDS works.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"step"},{"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-4.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"design system toolbox"}]},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox"}]}],"type":"step"},{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-discovery-6-5.png","type":"step","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS is open source, public and uses GitHub as forge. Thus, you will find common things inside the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"!"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"title":"More resources"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-onboarding-4-going-further"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"project","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"category":"Orange Unified Design System","categoryPathComponent":"Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)","role":"project","title":"Going further with more resources"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboar